---
title: Donate to The Texas Tribune
---

<% content_for :ie_styles do %>
  <!--[if IE 8]>-->
    <style>
      .splash {
        background-position: initial;
      }

      .splash-greeting {
        margin: 0;
      }
    </style>
  <!--<![endif]-->
<% end %>

<% content_for :main do %>
  <div class="splash">
    <div class="splash-wrapper">
      <div class="splash-greeting">
        <h1 class="splash-header">Show your support for independent, fact-based journalism by donating to The Texas Tribune.</h1>
        <p class="splash-info">As a 501(c)3 nonprofit organization, the generosity of members and donors makes our work possible. <a class="splash-link--yellow" href="https://www.texastribune.org/about/">Learn more</a> about the Tribune's mission.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="donate">
        <div class="donate__inner unloaded">
          <div id="carousel-outer" class="carousel">
            <form id="carousel-inner" class="carousel__form clearfix" action="" method="get" aria-labelledby="frequency-legend" role="form">
              <div class="carousel__slide--frequency">
                <fieldset class="carousel__fieldset">
                  <legend id="frequency-legend" class="carousel__legend">Donate today</legend>
                  <div class="carousel__radios">
                    <label class="carousel__label--selected" for="frequency-monthly">
                      <span class="uppercase weight--bold">Monthly</span>
                      <i class="carousel__checkmark fa fa-check-square" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                      <input id="frequency-monthly" class="carousel__radio visually-hidden" type="radio" value="monthly" name="frequency" data-frequency="monthly" checked onclick="ga('send', 'event', 'donations-app', 'click', 'frequency-monthly', {'nonInteraction': 1})">
                    </label>

                    <label class="carousel__label--normal" for="frequency-yearly">
                      <span class="uppercase weight--bold">Yearly</span>
                      <i class="carousel__checkmark fa fa-check-square" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                      <input id="frequency-yearly" class="carousel__radio visually-hidden" type="radio" value="yearly" name="frequency" data-frequency="yearly" onclick="ga('send', 'event', 'donations-app', 'click', 'frequency-yearly', {'nonInteraction': 1})">
                    </label>

                    <label class="carousel__label--normal" for="frequency-once">
                      <span class="uppercase weight--bold">One-Time</span>
                      <i class="carousel__checkmark fa fa-check-square" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                      <input id="frequency-once" class="carousel__radio visually-hidden" type="radio" value="once" name="frequency" data-frequency="once" onclick="ga('send', 'event', 'donations-app', 'click', 'frequency-once', {'nonInteraction': 1})">
                    </label>
                  </div>
                </fieldset>
              </div>

              <div class="carousel__slide--range" aria-hidden="true">
                <fieldset class="carousel__fieldset">
                  <legend id="range-legend" class="carousel__legend">I'm prepared to give&hellip;</legend>
                  <div class="carousel__radios">
                    <label class="carousel__label--selected" for="range-1">
                      <span class="weight--bold">Up to $35</span> per month
                      <i class="carousel__checkmark fa fa-check-square" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                      <input id="range-1" class="carousel__radio visually-hidden" type="radio" name="range" data-range="0" checked>
                    </label>

                    <label class="carousel__label--normal" for="range-2">
                      <span class="weight--bold">Up to $100</span> per month
                      <i class="carousel__checkmark fa fa-check-square" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                      <input id="range-2" class="carousel__radio visually-hidden" type="radio" name="range" data-range="1">
                    </label>

                    <label class="carousel__label--normal" for="range-3">
                      <span class="weight--bold">More than $100</span> per month
                      <i class="carousel__checkmark fa fa-check-square" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                      <input id="range-3" class="carousel__radio visually-hidden" type="radio" name="range" data-range="2">
                    </label>
                  </div>

                  <p class="carousel__student"><a class="splash-link--teal" href="https://checkout.texastribune.org/memberform?&amount=10&installmentPeriod=yearly">Interested</a> <span class="bold">in a $10 student membership?</span></p>
                </fieldset>
              </div>

              <div class="carousel__slide--amount" aria-hidden="true">
                <fieldset class="carousel__fieldset">
                  <legend id="amount-legend" class="carousel__legend">Choose an amount</legend>
                  <div class="carousel__radios">
                    <label class="carousel__label--normal" for="amount-1">
                      <span class="weight--bold">$12</span> per month
                      <i class="carousel__checkmark fa fa-check-square" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                      <input id="amount-1" class="carousel__radio visually-hidden" type="radio" value="12" name="amount">
                    </label>

                    <label class="carousel__label--selected" for="amount-2">
                      <span class="weight--bold">$25</span> per month
                      <i class="carousel__checkmark fa fa-check-square" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                      <input id="amount-2" class="carousel__radio visually-hidden" type="radio" value="25" name="amount" checked>
                    </label>

                    <label class="carousel__label--normal" for="amount-3">
                      <span class="weight--bold">$35</span> per month
                      <i class="carousel__checkmark fa fa-check-square" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                      <input id="amount-3" class="carousel__radio visually-hidden" type="radio" value="35" name="amount">
                    </label>
                  </div>

                  <div class="carousel__manual">
                    <div class="carousel__manual-els clearfix">
                      <label id="manual-label" class="carousel__manual-label" for="amount-manual">Or enter an amount:</label>
                      <input id="amount-manual" class="carousel__radio visually-hidden" type="radio" name="amount">
                      <input id="manual-input" class="carousel__manual-input--normal" type="text" aria-labelledby="manual-label" placeholder="$">
                    </div>

                    <p id="error-message" class="carousel__manual-error faux-hidden">Please enter a number.</p>
                  </div>
                </fieldset>

                <input id="submit" class="carousel__submit" aria-label="Go To Checkout" type="submit" value="Go To Checkout" onclick="ga('send', 'event', 'donations-app', 'click', 'go-to-checkout', {'nonInteraction': 1})">
              </div>
            </form>

            <div class="carousel__controls clearfix">
              <button id="prev" class="carousel__button--prev disabled" aria-label="Go back to previous screen" disabled onclick="ga('send', 'event', 'donations-app', 'click', 'checkout-back', {'nonInteraction': 1})">
                <i class="fa fa-long-arrow-left" aria-hidden="true"></i>&nbsp;Back
              </button>

              <ul class="carousel__indicators clearfix" aria-hidden="true">
                <li class="carousel__dot--selected"></li>
                <li class="carousel__dot--normal"></li>
                <li class="carousel__dot--normal"></li>
              </ul>

              <button id="next" class="carousel__button--next" aria-label="Move forward to next screen" onclick="ga('send', 'event', 'donations-app', 'click', 'checkout-next', {'nonInteraction': 1})">
                Next&nbsp;<i class="fa fa-long-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="donate__mail"><span class="weight--bold">Prefer to mail a check?</span> Use our <a class="splash-link--yellow" href="https://static.texastribune.org/media/marketing/TT-membership-contribution-form.pdf">membership form</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%= partial "desktop_nav" %>
  </div>

  <div class="main">
    <div class="main-left">
      <div class="section">
        <h3>All members enjoy the following benefits:</h3>
        <ul class="info-list">
          <li>Recognition on our <a href="https://www.texastribune.org/support-us/donors-and-members/">Donor Wall</a></li>
          <li>Discounted tickets to the annual <a href="https://www.texastribune.org/festival/">Texas Tribune Festival</a></li>
          <li>Exclusive, quarterly member e-newsletter, where you get a behind-the-scenes look at the Tribuneâ€™s latest projects and initiatives</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h3>Sustaining membership or a one-time?</h3>
        <ul class="info-list">
          <li>We think it's important that you get to support and consume the news on your own time and on your own terms. All donations are greatly appreciated!</li>
          <li>Members enjoy the benefits listed above.</li>
          <li>When you're a sustaining member, it simply means that your donation recurs automatically on a monthly or yearly basis via credit card. This provides the Tribune with the sort of predictable revenue that allows us to plan budgets a few years at a time, and it helps eliminate renewal mailings or lapses in your membership.</li>
          <li>Explore <a href="/levels.html">member levels</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <p class="student">
          <a href="https://checkout.texastribune.org/memberform?&amount=10&installmentPeriod=yearly">
            Interested in becoming a student member?
            <i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i>
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="main-right">
      <div class="section">
        <h3>Have a question?</h3>

        <div class="contact-info">
          <h5>Membership & The Blast</h5>
          <h4>Suzanne Geiger</h4>
          <p class="italic">Development Manager</p>
          <p>512-716-8646</p>
          <p><a href="mailto:sgeiger@texastribune.org">sgeiger@texastribune.org</a></p>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-info">
          <h4>Rebecca Quarls</h4>
          <p class="italic">Digital Marketing Manager</p>
          <p>512-716-8686</p>
          <p><a href="mailto:blast@texastribune.org">sgeiger@texastribune.org</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h3>Want to give more?</h3>

        <div class="give-more">
          <h5>Major gifts or grants</h5>
          <p>Please contact Terry Quinn at <a href="mailto:tquinn@texastribune.org">tquinn@texastribune.org</a> or call 512-716-8613</p>
        </div>

        <div class="give-more">
          <h5>Corporate sponsorships</h5>
          <p>Please contact April Hinkle at <a href="mailto:ahinkle@texastribune.org">ahinkle@texastribune.org</a> or call 512-716-8634</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

